<Body>
	<Title>目击者描述印尼爆炸案惨景 到处是炸断的肢体</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2002年10月13日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time type="absTime" tid="t1">2002年10月13日夜晚</Time>，<Location lid="l1">印尼旅游胜地巴厘岛</Location>发生连环恐怖<Denoter type="emergency" did="d1">爆炸</Denoter></Event>造成<Event eid="e2"><Participant oid="o2">202人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d2">丧生</Denoter></Event>，其中绝大部分是前来旅游的外国游客。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e3">印尼警察总监<Participant sid="s3">巴赫蒂亚尔</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d3">称</Denoter></Event>这次爆炸事件是该国历史上最严重的恐怖袭击事件，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e4"><Participant sid="s4">警方</Participant>没有立即<Denoter type="statement" did="d4">宣布</Denoter>袭击者的动机</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">中新网</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t5">10月13日</Time><Denoter type="statement" did="d5">电</Denoter>印度尼西亚巴厘岛消息</Event>，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">有关官员</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d6">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Time type="relTime" tid="t7">周六晚上</Time>印尼旅游胜地<Location lid="l7">巴厘岛</Location>连续发生几起<Denoter type="emergency" did="d7">爆炸</Denoter>事件</Event>，而且死者多数是外国人。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>直到周日凌晨，在上述夜总会的现场仍然是浓烟滚滚，直冲云宵，<Event eid="e8">与此同时<Participant sid="s8">警察</Participant>及<Participant  sid="s8">救援人员</Participant>将<Participant  oid="o8">受伤者和遇难者</Participant><Denoter type="action" did="d8">抬离</Denoter><Location lid="l8">现场</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e9">其中<Participant sid="s9">一些伤者</Participant>还在痛苦地<Denoter type="action" did="d9">呻吟</Denoter>着</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e10"><Participant sid="s10">警方</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d10">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11">预计还有<Participant oid="o11">一些伤者</Participant>被<Denoter type="action" did="d11">埋</Denoter>在<Location lid="l11">废墟</Location>下面</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e12">巴厘岛警方发言人<Participant sid="s12">亚蒂姆-苏亚特姆</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d12">表示</Denoter></Event>，警方认为所有的爆炸设备均为自制炸弹。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">一位当地的摄影师</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d13">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e14">发生爆炸的夜总会的<Object oid="o14">玻璃</Object>被<Denoter type="action" did="d14">炸</Denoter>到<Location lid="l14">比较远的地方</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="emergency" did="d15">爆炸</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e16">还导致附近<Object oid="o16">15辆汽车</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d16">被毁</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17">他</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d17">说</Denoter></Event>：“<Event eid="e18">整个<Object oid="o18">夜总会</Object>都被<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d18">夷为平地</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">我</Participant>都可以<Denoter type="perception" did="d19">闻到</Denoter>那些遇难者遗体发出的<Object oid="o19">臭味</Object></Event>。”</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e20">一位不愿透露姓名的<Participant sid="s20">警方官员</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d20">表示</Denoter></Event>：“<Event eid="e21">现在很难<Denoter type="perception" did="d21">辨认</Denoter>遇难者的<Object oid="o21">身份</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e22">因为他们的<Object oid="o22">遗体</Object>全都被<Denoter type="action" did="d22">炸</Denoter>得面目全非</Event>。”</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>爆炸发生时，在海边游玩的游客都在享受一个普通的周末，谁也没有想到灾难就在瞬间来临了。</Sentence><Sentence>
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e23"><Participant sid="s23">警方</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d23">称</Denoter></Event>，夜总会发生的爆炸给现场留下了一个大洞。</Sentence><Sentence>
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e24">上述那位<Participant sid="s24">摄影师</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d24">表示</Denoter></Event>：“
                <Event eid="e25"><Participant sid="s25">我</Participant><Denoter type="perception" did="d25">看到</Denoter>一个长得象是印尼人的<Participant oid="o25">男人</Participant></Event>，
                <Event eid="e26">他的<Object sid="s26">脑袋</Object>完全被<Denoter type="action" did="d26">炸</Denoter>得粉碎</Event>。”</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>今年37岁、来自新西兰的游客里查德-波雷是一位电视节目导演，<Event eid="e27"><Participant sid="s27">他</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d27">描述</Denoter>了当时的一些<Object oid="o27">情景</Object></Event>，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e28"><Participant sid="s28">他</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d28">说</Denoter></Event>：“<Event eid="e29"><Participant sid="s29">我</Participant><Denoter type="perception" did="d29">看到</Denoter>地面上到处都是被炸断的<Object  oid="o29">肢体</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e30">本来<Participant sid="s30">我</Participant>还想将<Object oid="o30">这些镜头</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d30">拍</Denoter>下来</Event>，<Event polarity="negative" eid="e31">但后来<Participant sid="s31">我</Participant>根本无法<Denoter type="action" did="d31">拍</Denoter>下去</Event>，因为现场简直成了一个屠杀场，<Event eid="e32"><Participant sid="s32">我</Participant>觉得非常<Denoter type="perception" did="d32">恶心</Denoter></Event>，<Event polarity="negative" eid="e33"><Participant sid="s33">我</Participant>在12年的拍摄生涯当中从未<Denoter type="perception" did="d33">见过</Denoter>这样惨的<Object oid="o33">死伤现场</Object></Event>。”</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e34"><Participant sid="s34">波雷</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d34">说</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e35"><Participant sid="s35">他</Participant>曾在爆炸发生前大约20分钟试图<Denoter type="movement" did="d35">进入</Denoter>那家<Location type="destination" lid="l35">夜总会</Location></Event>，但因为里面已经有几百名客人，非常拥挤，<Event polarity="negative" eid="e36">所以<Participant sid="s36">他</Participant>没能<Denoter  type="movement" did="d36">进去</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e37"><Participant sid="s37">另一名游客</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d37">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event polarity="negative" eid="e38">很多被吓坏了的<Participant sid="s38,s39">游客</Participant>都不再<Denoter did="d38" type="movement">进入</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l38">酒店房间</Location>休息</Event>而是<Event eid="e39">选择在<Location lid="l39">户外或是海滩上</Location><Denoter type="action" did="d39">睡觉</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e40"><Participant sid="s40">很多人</Participant>更是选择乘第一班能够离开巴厘岛的<means type="tool" mid="m40">飞机</means><Denoter type="movement" did="d40">返家</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
